devdoc.details: A dealer takes collateral and issues yDai. There is one Dealer per series.

addSeries(address).details: Adds an yDai series to this Dealer

borrow(uint256,address,uint256).details: Mint yDai for address `to` by locking its market value in collateral, user debt is increased.

containsSeries(uint256).details: Returns if a series has been added to the Dealer, for a given series identified by maturity

debtDai(uint256,address).details: Return debt in dai of an user, for a given series identified by maturity

inDai(uint256,uint256).details: Returns the dai equivalent of an yDai amount, for a given series identified by maturity

inYDai(uint256,uint256).details: Returns the yDai equivalent of a dai amount, for a given series identified by maturity

isCollateralized(address).details: Return if the borrowing power of an user is equal or greater than its debt

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

powerOf(address).details: Maximum borrowing power of an user in dai for a given collateral

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.     * NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

repayDai(uint256,address,uint256).details: Takes dai from `from` address, user debt is decreased.

repayYDai(uint256,address,uint256).details: Burns yDai from `from` address, user debt is decreased.

splitCollateral(address,address).details: Moves all weth from `from` in YDai to `to` in MakerDAO. Can only be called with no YDai debt. `to` needs to surround this call with `_vat.hope(address(_treasury))` and `_vat.nope(address(_treasury))`

splitPosition(uint256,address,address).details: Moves all debt for one series from `from` in YDai to `to` in MakerDAO. It also moves just enough weth from YDai to MakerDAO to enable the debt transfer. `to` needs to surround this call with `_vat.hope(address(_treasury))` and `_vat.nope(address(_treasury))`

totalDebtDai(address).details: Returns the total debt of an user, across all series, in Dai

totalDebtYDai(address).details: Returns the total debt of an user, across all series, in yDai

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.
